\par      *  2 Seats Occupied:\tab                 B S
\par }{\i\f38\insrsid14556939 
\par }{\f4\insrsid14556939 Similarly, post-flop position categories Early, Middle, Late, and Last are defined as follows:
\par 
\par      * 10 Players Left:\tab \tab E E E M M M M L L T
\par      *  9 Players Left:\tab \tab   E E E M M M L L T
\par      *  8 Players Left:\tab \tab     E E M M M L L T
\par      *  7 Players Left:\tab \tab       E E M M L L T
